INSERT INTO program_sops (module_id, sop_number, title, content, quality_bars, deliverables, tools_used, dependencies, version)
VALUES (
  'm1',
  '1-1',
  'Ideate a Lead Magnet with Magnet Lab',
  $body$## Steps
1. Open Magnet Lab Ideator tool.
2. The tool will "grill" you with questions about your expertise, clients, and problems you solve. Answer thoroughly — more context = better ideas.
3. Paste in supporting material: client call transcripts, website content, past posts that performed well, case studies.

:::info Real-World Example
You almost certainly already have lead magnets — you just haven't packaged them yet. Mine coaching call recordings, onboarding documents, audits, templates, frameworks, and training materials. The single best source: your sales calls. Whatever you explain that makes a prospect's eyes light up is exactly what your lead magnet should be about. Magnet Lab connects to meeting note-takers like Fathom to extract transcripts automatically, continuously updating your knowledge base so new lead magnets and LinkedIn posts can be generated on demand from real conversations.
:::

:::tip From the Field
Look at deliverables your business already creates for clients — reports, summaries, decks — and model your lead magnet after those formats. This ensures the lead magnet feels familiar and legitimate to your target audience. Lead magnet format must match how your ideal clients consume information day-to-day: formal reports and documents for traditional industries like claims management, fancy interactive tools for audiences that love shiny objects. Don't default to flashy formats unless that matches your audience.
:::

:::info Real-World Example
Magnet Lab is a free tool that creates lead magnets and landing pages, including complete funnels (landing page, thank you page), content pages with videos and qualification forms leading to call booking, and a theme builder for customization. It integrates with Lead Shock, features a Notion-like editor for hosting, and can extract content from call transcripts or any data input to automatically generate lead magnet content and funnels. You can also import existing lead magnets and pages via API.
:::

4. Review the generated lead magnet concepts. Each will include a title, format suggestion, and angle.
5. Pick the concept that feels most aligned with your Caroline's #1 problem.
6. If nothing fits, refine your inputs and regenerate. The quality of output directly reflects the quality of input.

:::warning Common Question
**"What if the AI-generated lead magnet ideas don't match what I actually do?"** Scrap or adapt — never publish a lead magnet you can't confidently discuss with a prospect. Paste the original idea back into the Lead Magnet Ideator, specify what doesn't resonate, and have it regenerate something closer to your real methodology. A lead magnet should deliver one immediately implementable quick win you're proud of.
:::

:::info Real-World Example
The platform has three distinct AI tools for the lead magnet workflow: (1) **Lead Magnet Ideator** — adapts a concept based on what you don't resonate with; (2) **Lead Magnet Creator** — turns an approved idea into the actual deliverable asset; (3) **Lead Magnet Post Creator** — generates the LinkedIn post to promote it. These are accessible via email login independent of bootcamp enrollment.
:::

:::tip From the Field
Magnet Lab now supports quiz, scorecard, and custom GPT lead magnet formats — not just static pages. When the AI recommends an interactive format, the tool will actually build it (quizzes with scored, differentiated answers; custom GPTs as self-hosted prompts with a UI). Feature is new — give feedback if output doesn't match the recommended format.
::::$body$,
  '[{"check":"Lead magnet concept must be confidently defensible and discussable with a prospect — never publish ideas you cannot explain","severity":"critical"},{"check":"Lead magnet format must match how target audience actually consumes information (formal reports for traditional industries, interactive tools for modern audiences)","severity":"critical"},{"check":"Input quality directly determines output quality — provide thorough answers, transcripts, case studies, and supporting materials","severity":"warning"},{"check":"Lead magnet should deliver one immediately implementable quick win aligned with target''s #1 problem","severity":"warning"},{"check":"Leverage existing business deliverables (reports, audits, templates, call recordings) rather than creating from scratch","severity":"info"}]'::jsonb,
  '[{"type":"lead_magnet","description":"An ideated lead magnet concept with title, format suggestion, and angle that aligns with the target audience''s primary problem"}]'::jsonb,
  ARRAY['magnetlab_ideator', 'fathom']::text[],
  ARRAY[]::text[],
  1
)
