INSERT INTO program_sops (module_id, sop_number, title, content, quality_bars, deliverables, tools_used, dependencies, version)
VALUES (
  'm1',
  '1-2',
  'Create a Lead Magnet Asset',
  $body$:::info Build Context
:::

## Steps

1. Take your chosen concept from the Ideator and open Magnet Lab Creator.

:::tip From the Field
You likely already have many lead magnet assets without realizing it — solution proposals, internal prompts, frameworks you've walked clients through, and materials your team already uses. These existing assets can be quickly packaged into lead magnet formats rather than starting from scratch. Once created, a single lead magnet becomes the central asset for all B2B distribution: social posts, DMs, cold email, and paid ads — so the ability to create these repeatedly and systematically is crucial for go-to-market success.
:::

2. The Creator will generate the lead magnet asset (PDF, checklist, template, guide, etc.).
3. Review every section. Edit for accuracy — the tool gives you structure and first-draft copy, but your expertise makes it credible.
4. Keep it concise. Almost nobody reads the whole thing. They scan for key insights, then decide if you're worth talking to.
5. Export the finished asset as a PDF or the appropriate format.
6. Name it clearly: "[Topic] — [Format]" (e.g., "LinkedIn Lead Gen Playbook — Checklist").$body$,
  '[{"check":"Lead magnet asset must be reviewed and edited for accuracy by subject matter expert before export","severity":"critical"},{"check":"Asset must be concise and scannable — key insights should be immediately apparent, not buried in lengthy text","severity":"critical"},{"check":"Asset must be exported in appropriate format (PDF, checklist, template, or guide) with clear naming convention","severity":"critical"},{"check":"Asset should leverage existing internal materials (proposals, frameworks, prompts) rather than creating entirely from scratch","severity":"warning"}]'::jsonb,
  '[{"type":"lead_magnet","description":"Completed lead magnet asset (PDF, checklist, template, or guide) with clear naming and ready for distribution across multiple channels"}]'::jsonb,
  ARRAY['magnetlab_ideator', 'magnetlab_creator']::text[],
  ARRAY['1-1']::text[],
  1
)
