INSERT INTO program_sops (module_id, sop_number, title, content, quality_bars, deliverables, tools_used, dependencies, version)
VALUES (
  'm1',
  '1-3',
  'Build the Lead Magnet Funnel',
  $body$:::info Build Context
:::

## Steps

1. Create an opt-in page using Magnet Lab Pages (or GoHighLevel / Kit / Webflow).

:::warning Common Question
**"Does the funnel live on a separate platform or on the client's own website?"** Magnet Lab builds and hosts the opt-in page, thank you page, and delivery page, but it connects to and lives as an extension of the client's existing web presence — not on a separate domain.
:::

2. The opt-in page collects their email address. Do NOT give them the lead magnet here.

3. After opt-in, redirect to a Thank You page. This page must include: (a) a video of you explaining your service and who it's for, (b) qualification questions or criteria, (c) a calendar booking link for qualified prospects.

4. The Thank You page is NOT the lead magnet. It's your best shot at converting while you have their attention.

5. Set up email delivery: the lead magnet is sent via email (not on the page). Use Loops, Kit, GoHighLevel, or Mailchimp.

6. Build a 5-email nurture sequence using Magnet Lab Email Writer: Email 1 = deliver asset + personal note. Email 2 = the problem this solves. Email 3 = why solve it now. Email 4 = why you're the right person. Email 5 = case study or social proof + CTA.

7. Configure email timing: space emails 1–2 days apart. Do NOT send all 5 quickly — high complaint rates.

:::tip From the Field
One of the most powerful approaches is **"let me help you build what I just did to you."** If you have technical skills (e.g., Webflow development, AI automation), use those same skills to create the lead magnet funnel itself. When prospects book a call, you can say: *"You got on this call because I made you this crazy custom landing page — I can build you one too."* This turns your funnel into a live demo of your capabilities. Magnet Lab simplifies this further — unlike GoHighLevel, which requires manual setup each time, Magnet Lab is fully API-programmable, letting you import existing lead magnets and deploy complete funnels (qualification questions, thank you pages, videos, and 5-email sequences) with one click.
::::$body$,
  '[{"check":"Lead magnet asset is NOT delivered on opt-in page; must be sent via email only","severity":"critical"},{"check":"Thank You page includes video explanation, qualification criteria, and calendar booking link","severity":"critical"},{"check":"5-email nurture sequence follows prescribed structure (asset delivery, problem, urgency, authority, proof)","severity":"warning"},{"check":"Email timing is spaced 1–2 days apart to avoid high complaint/unsubscribe rates","severity":"warning"},{"check":"Funnel integration connects to client''s existing web presence, not a separate domain","severity":"info"}]'::jsonb,
  '[{"type":"funnel","description":"Complete lead magnet funnel including opt-in page, thank you page with video and qualification questions, email delivery infrastructure, and 5-email nurture sequence"}]'::jsonb,
  ARRAY['magnetlab_funnel_builder', 'magnetlab_post_writer']::text[],
  ARRAY['1-1', '1-2']::text[],
  1
)
