INSERT INTO program_sops (module_id, sop_number, title, content, quality_bars, deliverables, tools_used, dependencies, version)
VALUES (
  'm1',
  '1-4',
  'Write and Publish a Lead Magnet LinkedIn Post',
  $body$:::info Build Context
:::

## Steps

1. Open Magnet Lab Post Writer. It will generate 3 post variants for your lead magnet.
2. Review all 3 variants. Pick the one that best matches your voice and your Caroline's language.
3. Edit the post: add your personal angle, refine the hook, make the CTA clear ("Comment [keyword] and I'll send it over").
4. Publish to LinkedIn.
5. Do NOT include a direct link to the lead magnet in the post. The CTA should drive comments, not clicks. Comments trigger your DM automation.
6. You can repost the same lead magnet every 6 weeks for the rest of your life. Winning posts are evergreen.

:::tip From the Field
The dominant lead magnet post template on LinkedIn was copied by course sellers, packaged into programs, and spread to thousands of users — the feed is saturated with clones. Don't emotionally attach to the feed or resent the saturation; treat LinkedIn as a tool, use what works, and detach from the noise.
:::

:::tip From the Field
LinkedIn posts are just one channel. A single lead magnet becomes a multi-channel asset — use it in cold emails ("Hey, I made this resource, thought it might interest you"), LinkedIn DMs, LinkedIn and Facebook ads, email campaigns to your existing list, and community sharing. This is one of the highest-leverage activities in your business because every channel becomes a value exchange, not just an ask.
:::$body$,
  '[{"check":"CTA must drive comments, not direct clicks—no direct lead magnet link in post","severity":"critical"},{"check":"Post must match creator''s voice and brand language, not generic template","severity":"warning"},{"check":"Personal angle and hook refinement applied before publishing","severity":"warning"},{"check":"Lead magnet is positioned as multi-channel asset for reuse across 6+ weeks","severity":"info"}]'::jsonb,
  '[{"type":"post_drafts","description":"LinkedIn post variants generated by Magnet Lab Post Writer, reviewed and edited with personal angle and clear comment-driven CTA"},{"type":"email_campaign","description":"Lead magnet asset repurposed across multiple channels including cold emails, LinkedIn DMs, ads, and email list campaigns"}]'::jsonb,
  ARRAY['magnetlab_post_writer']::text[],
  ARRAY['1-1', '1-2', '1-3']::text[],
  1
)
