:::tip From the Field
When requesting your data, select **Request new Archive** and choose the **larger data archive** — not just Connections. Within 24 hours you'll receive a zip file containing ~20 CSVs, including every connection, every message sent/received, and every post you've made. This is powerful because it reveals hundreds of ideal-fit clients already in your network who have simply fallen off your radar.
