INSERT INTO program_sops (module_id, sop_number, title, content, quality_bars, deliverables, tools_used, dependencies, version)
VALUES (
  'm2',
  '2-2',
  'Build a Sales Navigator Search for Your TAM',
  $body$## Build Context

## Steps

1. Open LinkedIn Sales Navigator.

:::tip From the Field
Sales Navigator (~$100/month) pays for itself two ways: (1) it lets you filter for active users — 99% of LinkedIn accounts are inactive, so without this filter, connection request acceptance rates crater; (2) being a paying LinkedIn customer gives you platform protection — LinkedIn is less likely to ban or rate-limit paying accounts, and you'll see higher action limits, better feed surfacing, and greater overall platform favor.
:::

2. Create a new Lead search.
3. Apply filters to match your Caroline Framework: job title, industry, company size, geography, seniority level.
4. **CRITICAL:** Toggle the "Posted on LinkedIn in the past 30 days" filter ON. This is the single most important filter — it separates people who will see your messages from people who won't.
5. Review the results. Aim for 10,000–30,000 contacts for a healthy TAM.
6. Save this search as a named list in Sales Navigator.
7. Export the list using HeyReach or a Sales Navigator export tool.

:::tip From the Field
Sales Navigator exports alone are too inaccurate and general to act on without validation. Use a multi-tool approach: generate target companies/contacts with Claude, export from Sales Nav, then run both through a semantic matching tool like Disco Like (which matches against website text) to validate and enrich. The resulting list will be smaller but significantly more precise.
:::$body$,
  '[{"check":"\"Posted on LinkedIn in the past 30 days\" filter must be toggled ON to ensure contacts are active and will see outreach messages","severity":"critical"},{"check":"Final TAM list size should be 10,000–30,000 contacts for a healthy, actionable segment","severity":"warning"},{"check":"All Caroline Framework filters (job title, industry, company size, geography, seniority) must be applied and documented","severity":"warning"},{"check":"Sales Navigator exports should be validated and enriched using semantic matching tools before use to improve list precision and accuracy","severity":"info"}]'::jsonb,
  '[{"type":"tam_segment","description":"A filtered, saved Sales Navigator search list of 10,000–30,000 active contacts matching the Caroline Framework criteria, exported and validated for outreach readiness"}]'::jsonb,
  ARRAY['sales_navigator', 'heyreach']::text[],
  ARRAY[]::text[],
  1
)
