  $body$## Steps
1. In your Clay table, click Add New Column → Waterfall.
2. Select data type: Email.
3. Add providers in this order (cheapest to most expensive): (1) ICPS — cheapest, requires full name + company domain. (2) LeadMagic / Find Work Email. (3) Kit. (4) Prospeo / Find Email — most expensive, use as fallback.
