## Steps

1. Identify a segment of your existing connections who match your ICP.
2. Create a new HeyReach campaign targeting this segment.
3. Write a message offering your lead magnet: "Hey [first_name], I just put together [lead magnet name] for [niche]. Want me to send it over?"
4. Set the campaign to run.
5. When someone says yes, send them the opt-in link (not the PDF directly — you want their email).
6. This feeds them into your lead magnet funnel (opt-in → thank you page → email sequence).$body$,
