INSERT INTO program_sops (module_id, sop_number, title, content, quality_bars, deliverables, tools_used, dependencies, version)
VALUES (
  'm3',
  '3-4',
  'Handle a High-Value Prospect Response',
  $body$:::info Build Context
:::

## Steps

1. When a high-value prospect (large company, big budget, perfect ICP match) responds to any channel, drop the automation immediately.
2. Research them manually: check their website, recent posts, company news, team size, funding.
3. Record a personalized Loom video (60–90 seconds) addressing them by name, referencing something specific about their business, and explaining one opportunity you see for them.
4. Send the video via DM along with the lead magnet they requested: "Here's the [asset]. I also put together a quick video with some thoughts specifically for [company name]."
5. If they engage with the video, offer to hop on a call. If they don't respond, follow up once after 3–5 days with a different angle.$body$,
